{"tid":17841,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人中左ielts伏","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T11:15:54.000Z","uid":28483,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"417fa136ee298a22f40a9c9cb4cecd36b698165d","tid":17841,"uid":28483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"一開始勁多電話打過黎sell我都無理嘅 但之後有個幾fd報左 叫我去試埋堂 咁就瀨左野啦<br />\n佢個試堂就係到講話咩你dse得3 ielts course可以補你有6.5以上 咁你gpa就可以高啲 仲入到ugc<br />\n仲話咩無6.5就可以免費take多次個course<br />\n跟住我就on99交左錢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家上到第三期 見到有post話ielts大伏先醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自認on9中左伏 唔知點算好依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經交左萬幾銀但唔想再俾班仆街呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認住下期唔撚報 自己做pp好過<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs. 試左堂交左一期錢睇下有無得退 無就上完一期好快quit 唔係會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想報course個啲就自己衡量下 一星期2堂 一堂3個鐘 一個月3400 仲要教啲簡單野 <br />\n我英交算差但佢上堂啲練習都啱足7成半 可想而知佢教啲野有幾簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8adb1dbc5bbe9a2e3ed972fe83621b6269759a4","tid":17841,"uid":45696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開始勁多電話打過黎sell我都無理嘅 但之後有個幾fd報左 叫我去試埋堂 咁就瀨左野啦<br />\n佢個試堂就係到講話咩你dse得3 ielts course可以補你有6.5以上 咁你gpa就可以高啲 仲入到ugc<br />\n仲話咩無6.5就可以免費take多次個course<br />\n跟住我就on99交左錢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家上到第三期 見到有post話ielts大伏先醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自認on9中左伏 唔知點算好依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經交左萬幾銀但唔想再俾班仆街呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認住下期唔撚報 自己做pp好過<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs. 試左堂交左一期錢睇下有無得退 無就上完一期好快quit 唔係會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想報course個啲就自己衡量下 一星期2堂 一堂3個鐘 一個月3400 仲要教啲簡單野 <br />\n我英交算差但佢上堂啲練習都啱足7成半 可想而知佢教啲野有幾簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打試堂果時冇發覺其他人試堂既內容同自己一模一樣架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫埋身邊既fd同同班既fd quit啦<br />\n又學唔到野又繼續比班狗呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223a957a661826d9ba5b6c3ae0b60685f08fb963","tid":17841,"uid":28483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一開始勁多電話打過黎sell我都無理嘅 但之後有個幾fd報左 叫我去試埋堂 咁就瀨左野啦<br />\n佢個試堂就係到講話咩你dse得3 ielts course可以補你有6.5以上 咁你gpa就可以高啲 仲入到ugc<br />\n仲話咩無6.5就可以免費take多次個course<br />\n跟住我就on99交左錢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家上到第三期 見到有post話ielts大伏先醒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自認on9中左伏 唔知點算好依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經交左萬幾銀但唔想再俾班仆街呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認住下期唔撚報 自己做pp好過<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPs. 試左堂交左一期錢睇下有無得退 無就上完一期好快quit 唔係會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想報course個啲就自己衡量下 一星期2堂 一堂3個鐘 一個月3400 仲要教啲簡單野 <br />\n我英交算差但佢上堂啲練習都啱足7成半 可想而知佢教啲野有幾簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打試堂果時冇發覺其他人試堂既內容同自己一模一樣架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫埋身邊既fd同同班既fd quit啦<br />\n又學唔到野又繼續比班狗呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個陣班房一對一 唔知人地係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同我同班嘅fd諗住quit 勁後悔俾左三期錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15745988b84a33dc4af6e2e853e13b2e44fe6629","tid":17841,"uid":28483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"仲要調堂就要隔幾個月先有得上番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一係俾45蚊睇dvd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4ac41678c9fc1a09485468da64c8c01bf047ee","tid":17841,"uid":28483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04987befe85b7d2053d8467da0f1a5f00b473b0","tid":17841,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"成皮野上ielts堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9df08347d446c946749c86ae3f044be6639325e","tid":17841,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成皮野上ielts堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夠考幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03dc863465d076144cacb5a2eabbfe5f8f66d862","tid":17841,"uid":28483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成皮野上ielts堂<i