d954fad1f82a9ba2c2f64d3c080","tid":17841,"uid":28483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點算 交咗$3000 但未開始上堂<br />\n有無得退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以，不過要企定同佢拗"},{"pid":"69668b34592e269b51284e3339c12b36122c35b3","tid":17841,"uid":46551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:21:53.000Z","msg":"ielts 都要上堂?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm"},{"pid":"185c8049f6ea841904d97adf905f789ec40e7f47","tid":17841,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個時上去試堂<br />\n佢會搵難字考你+搵份reading比你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就廢嘅，字就唔識<br />\n不過reading撞中幾條喇<br />\n佢就叫我讀讀<br />\n<br />\n走個時有個自稱hku嘅人同我吹水<br />\n話咩啲字佢都唔識，比條友串佢<br />\n問佢係咪hku<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過reading 佢啱哂，<br />\n之後佢話個seller 唔敢比佢睇答案<br />\n直接skip咗<br />\n之後條友同我講，啲人都幾廢<br />\n叫我唔好報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有佢問我中文點？<br />\n我話ok喇，之後佢寫個鯉，鯨問我點讀<br />\n最後寫個鮢字問我點讀<br />\n之後鮢字我諗咗陣<br />\n話唔識（雖然估係朱，不過唔肯定嘅喇我唔答）<br />\n佢就串我話其實佢亂寫出嚟，話我中文差<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網睇返，好嬲啊<br />\n我都冇錯<br />\n<br />\n（雖然佢都係想講英文拆字，是但搵例子）"}]}